Zorin (Ubuntu) Equivalent:

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:vala-panel/ppa
sudo apt update
sudo apt install vala-panel vala-panel-appmenu appmenu-gtk2-module appmenu-gtk3-module appmenu-registrar

Zorin Equivalent (same command, works fine):

xfconf-query -c xsettings -p /Gtk/ShellShowsMenubar -n -t bool -s true
xfconf-query -c xsettings -p /Gtk/ShellShowsAppmenu -n -t bool -s true
âœ… These commands activate the global menu system inside XFCE.

